{"tid":1630321,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線手足 Twitter 唔好用自己相","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:04:53.000Z","uid":22407,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73125f1ce068418e568150cd19907e8115dbf91f","tid":1630321,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"各位幫手係Twitter 做文宣嘅手足<br />\n唔好再用自己相同慣用user name <br />\n最好少提及自己事<br />\n免得俾班外國5毛起底<br />\n一切要小心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#fightforfreedom <br />\n#standwithhk </span></span>"},{"pid":"bbd301cd9d7a3195a5dab2d6b7080161f8ca5af0","tid":1630321,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bff7785428adf780573cbb9273c515f1c9a8160b","tid":1630321,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好用藍絲啲樣做profile呀</span>"},{"pid":"0763fd428dcc39f6ae42db43d244d6c1a376fa84","tid":1630321,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjoq1qT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjoq1qT.png&h=c361cab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外 大家唔好post 山埃比solomon / 其他senator啦<br />\n有好多FCed係錯嘅"},{"pid":"d0ac0ef8404e2a5591c16e603c8f5b0b245bb4ec","tid":1630321,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0763fd428dcc39f6ae42db43d244d6c1a376fa84","tid":1630321,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjoq1qT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjoq1qT.png&h=c361cab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外 大家唔好post 山埃比solomon / 其他senator啦<br />\n有好多FCed係錯嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好心急想俾其他人知香港係點<br />\n但真係嘅嘢 影響大局先推俾solomon yue睇<br />\n成日@人都會覺得煩 <br />\n而且好大機會miss最重要嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791193f1daa500ef8216cf6efbc26975fa56581d","tid":1630321,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0ac0ef8404e2a5591c16e603c8f5b0b245bb4ec","tid":1630321,"uid":22407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0763fd428dcc39f6ae42db43d244d6c1a376fa84","tid":1630321,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjoq1qT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frjoq1qT.png&h=c361cab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外 大家唔好post 山埃比solomon / 其他senator啦<br />\n有好多FCed係錯嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"我知大家都好心急想俾其他人知香港係點<br />\n但真係嘅嘢 影響大局先推俾solomon yue睇<br 